title: Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,439 Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series (Yahoo Sports) One final, charmed swing by Daniel Murphy, and the New York Mets finished a playoff sweep of the Chicago Cubs. A new generation of Amazins is heading to the World Series. Murphy homered for a record sixth consecutive postseason game and the Mets brushed aside the Cubs 8-3 Wednesday night, capping a National League Championship Series in which New York never trailed.
